data.description: Introducing a Sun City West, Arizona Gemini unit nestled on the picturesque Pebblebrook golf course. As you approach the property, there is large gated front courtyard with covered entry. HOA maintains the landscaped front yard. The heart of this home is the large living room. Enjoy the golf course views through the adjacent large Arizona room sliding doors.  The galley kitchen with upgraded appliances opens to a breakfast nook and an area that could be used for crafts or as an office. There are two bedrooms. The master has golf course views. Both bathrooms have walk-in showers. The master bath is ensuite and has an updated vanity. The washer and dryer are located inside the garage. Two-car garage with built- in storage cabinets.
